'''橘腿管蚜蝇'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Eristalis flavipes''}})，是[[双翅目|双翅目]][[食蚜蝇科|食蚜蝇科]]下的一[[物种|种]][[昆虫|昆虫]]。
==分布==
本种分布于[[北美洲|北美洲]]
<ref>{{cite web
|url=http://www.americaninsects.net/f/eristalis-flavipes.html
|title=Eristalis flavipes Drone Fly / Hover Fly
|publisher=American Insects
|access-date=2021-02-21
|archive-date=2012-03-18
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120318184555/http://www.americaninsects.net/f/eristalis-flavipes.html
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>。

==描述==
成虫长约15毫米。[[拟态|形似]][[熊蜂|熊蜂]]，但它的跗节是橘色，故名“橘腿管蚜蝇”
<ref>{{cite web
|url=https://www.fs.fed.us/wildflowers/pollinators/pollinator-of-the-month/drone_flies.shtml
|title=Drone Flies
|publisher=US Forest Service
|access-date=2021-02-21
|archive-date=2021-04-01
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210401170520/https://www.fs.fed.us/wildflowers/pollinators/pollinator-of-the-month/drone_flies.shtml
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>。

幼虫腹部尾端有个长的呼吸虹管，这种蛆称为“[[鼠尾蛆|鼠尾蛆]]”
<ref>{{cite web
|url=https://ffnaturesearch.org/eristalis-flavipes/
|title=ERISTALIS FLAVIPES
|publisher=Fontenelle Nature Association
}}</ref>。
